gource
------------------------------------------
OpenGL-based 3D visualisation tool for source control repositories.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.0.7-1
  libboost_filesystem1.66-1.66.0-1
  libboost_system1.66-1.66.0-1
  libfreetype6-2.8.1-1
  libgcc1-7.4.0-1
  libGLEW2.1-2.1.0-1
  libpcre1-8.43-1
  libpng16-1.6.34-1
  libSDL2_2.0_0-2.0.7-1
  libSDL2_image2.0_0-2.0.2-1
  libstdc++6-7.4.0-1
  libtinyxml0-2.6.2-1bl3

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  autoconf-13-1
  automake-10-1
  binutils-2.29-1
  cygport-0.33.1-1
  gcc-core-7.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-7.4.0-1
  make-4.2.1-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/acaudwell/Gource

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/acaudwell/Gource/releases/download/gource-0.49/gource-0.49.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack gource-0.49-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./gource-0.49-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/gource-0.49-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/gource-0.49-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(gource)
  /usr/bin/gource.exe
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/gource.README
  /usr/share/doc/gource/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/gource/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/gource/README
  /usr/share/doc/gource/THANKS
  /usr/share/gource/beam.png
  /usr/share/gource/bloom.tga
  /usr/share/gource/bloom_alpha.tga
  /usr/share/gource/file.png
  /usr/share/gource/fonts/FreeSans.ttf
  /usr/share/gource/fonts/README
  /usr/share/gource/gource.style
  /usr/share/gource/shaders/bloom.frag
  /usr/share/gource/shaders/bloom.vert
  /usr/share/gource/shaders/shadow.frag
  /usr/share/gource/shaders/shadow.vert
  /usr/share/gource/shaders/text.frag
  /usr/share/gource/shaders/text.vert
  /usr/share/gource/user.png
  /usr/share/man/man1/gource.1.gz

